/* FancyThumbs MediaWiki extension   *
 * Version: 1.2 (Tue, 21 Aug 2012)   *
 * Author: weiss, http://ndmitry.ru/ *
 * E-mail: dima.nikitenko@gmail.com  *
 * Testing only on MediaWiki 1.19.1! */

Example:
    http://stalkerworld.ru/wiki/

Installation:
    1. Download the files from here: https://github.com/nDmitry/FancyThumbs/zipball/master
    2. Create a directory FancyThumbs in your $IP/extensions directory
    3. Extract the files to this $IP/extensions/FancyThumbs directory
    4. Add to the end of LocalSettings.php:
        require_once("$IP/extensions/FancyThumbs/FancyThumbs.php");
    
    Installation can now be verified through Special:Version on your wiki.